Tara Palmeri: How do you see the future of your party?

Max Rose: I think we have to diagnose what actually happened here; it=E2=80=
=99s not some abject denunciation of the Democratic Party. In fact, 2016 an=
d 2020 were more like that. In =E2=80=9916 and =E2=80=9920, the Democrats d=
id not win a single statewide race in a state that Trump won; this year, we=
 won four.

