, the simplicity of his messaging is critical. There=E2=80=99s no doubt he=
=E2=80=99s good at branding. The other thing that is not as often acknowled=
ged about the Trump campaign is it very clearly sought to engage in cultura=
l communication and cultural trust-building, whether he=E2=80=99s walking o=
ut at a UFC fight or going to the varied podcasts.

One of the hopes is that
the Democratic Party will begin to understand that voting is not always an =
act of self-interest, but also an act of self-expression. And if we complet=
ely ignore that element of decision-making, we=E2=80=99ll continue to fall =
short. We have the country largely unified around what we=E2=80=99re doing,=
 but not feeling like they=E2=80=99re emotionally, culturally, and psycholo=
gically aligned with where we are as people. And that=E2=80=99s something w=
e can fix.

