 me</a></u> recently, =E2=80=9CIf you lost, you have no business telling th=
e party how to win.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>Rose does have some ideas, though, an=
d he also thinks 2024 wasn=E2=80=99t the =E2=80=9Cabject denunciation=E2=80=
=9D of the party that many observers have described it as. He suggested tha=
